  "bug_summary": "createContext 创建时固化 model 快照，扩展后续读取不到模型变更",
  "module": "extensions-runner",
  "action": "createContext",
  "fix_summary": "将 model 属性改为 getter，通过 getModel() 动态读取当前模型",
  "test_type": "regression",
  "boundary": "service",
  "wrong_behavior": "扩展上下文的 model 始终是创建时的快照，模型切换后不更新",
